<span id="Description"></span>
==Popis==

The '''Std DlgPreferences''' command opens the [[Preferences_Editor|Preferences Editor]].

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Použití==

# There are several ways to invoke the command:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Edit → [[Image:Std_DlgPreferences.svg|16px]] Preferences}} option from the menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|Ctrl}}+{{KEY|,}}. {{Version|1.1}}

<span id="Notes"></span>
==Poznámky==

* For more information see [[Preferences_Editor|Preferences Editor]].
* On macOS this command may appear in the FreeCAD menu instead of the [[Std_Edit_Menu|Edit]] menu.


